1. *Svinje* su glavni izvor proteina za neke ljude. (*Pigs* are the main source of protein for some people.)
2. Ne volim kad mi se *svinje* penju po ogradi. (I don't like it when *pigs* climb on my fence.)
3. Na farmi ima petnaestak *svinja*. (There are about fifteen *pigs* on the farm.)
4. Stajalište za *svinje* nalazi se na kraju voza. (The *pig* compartment is located at the end of the train.)
5. Sinoć sam u restoranu jeo pečenog odojka, to je bio najbolji *svinjski* file koji sam ikada probao. (Last night, I had roasted suckling pig at the restaurant, it was the best *pork* fillet I've ever tasted.)
6. Moja baka svake godine sprema *svinjsku* mast za zimu. (My grandmother makes *lard* every year for the winter.)
7. *Svinjsko* meso se često koristi za pripremu raznih jela. (*Pork* is often used in the preparation of various dishes.)
8. Vozač kamiona je prevozio *žive svinje* do mesare. (The truck driver was transporting *live pigs* to the slaughterhouse.)
9. Komšija se bavi uzgojem *svinja* za prodaju mesa. (My neighbor breeds *pigs* for meat production.)
10. *Svinjski* odresci su jedno od mojih omiljenih jela. (*Pork* chops are one of my favorite dishes.)